	 (69,9,'Waldorf Astoria Edinburgh – The Caledonian','Princes Street, Edinburgh EH1 2AB, United Kingdom','A cornerstone of Edinburgh`s luxury scene, Waldorf Astoria Edinburgh combines timeless elegance with contemporary flair. Known for its historic architecture and impeccable service, the hotel has hosted royalty, celebrities, and discerning travelers alike. Guests can indulge in gourmet dining and unwind in the luxurious spa.',1100.0,341),
	 (70,9,'The Witchery by the Castle','352 Castlehill, Edinburgh EH1 2NF, United Kingdom','Overlooking the Royal Mile, The Witchery by the Castle is a blend of Gothic and Baroque design, offering guests a unique and luxurious experience. With a history of hosting illustrious figures, the hotel boasts exceptional dining options and a renowned atmosphere. Its central location provides easy access to Edinburgh`s cultural landmarks.',950.0,346),
	 (71,9,'Prestonfield House','Priestfield Road, Edinburgh EH16 5UT, United Kingdom','Nestled in the heart of Edinburgh, Prestonfield House is a blend of classic Scottish charm and contemporary sophistication. The hotel features elegantly appointed rooms, a Michelin-starred restaurant, and the world-famous Rhubarb Restaurant. Its commitment to personalized service ensures a memorable stay for every guest.',1000.0,351),
	 (72,10,'The Ritz-Carlton, Vienna','Schubertring 5-7, 1010 Vienna, Austria','Housed in four historic 19th-century palaces, The Ritz-Carlton, Vienna seamlessly blends imperial grandeur with contemporary luxury. Situated on the iconic Ringstraße, it offers guests opulent rooms, a rooftop bar with panoramic city views, and a luxurious spa.',1200.0,356),
	 (73,10,'Hotel Sacher Wien','Philharmoniker Str. 4, 1010 Vienna, Austria','A Viennese institution since 1876, Hotel Sacher Wien is renowned for its timeless elegance and the original Sachertorte. Located opposite the State Opera, it offers guests luxurious rooms adorned with original artwork and antiques, alongside impeccable service.​',1300.0,361),
	 (74,10,'Park Hyatt Vienna','Am Hof 2, 1010 Vienna, Austria','Set in a former bank building dating back to 1913, Park Hyatt Vienna combines historic charm with modern luxury. Located in the Goldenes Quartier, it offers guests spacious rooms with high ceilings, a tranquil spa, and fine dining options.​',1100.0,366),
	 (75,10,'Hotel Imperial, a Luxury Collection Hotel','Kärntner Ring 16, 1015 Vienna, Austria','Originally built as a palace in 1863, Hotel Imperial offers guests a regal experience with its opulent interiors and exceptional service. Located on the Ringstraße, it provides easy access to Vienna`s cultural landmarks and shopping districts.​',1250.0,371);
