	 (80,12,'Sense Hotel Sofia','16 Tsar Osvoboditel Blvd, 1000 Sofia, Bulgaria','Located on Sofia’s iconic boulevard, Sense Hotel is the city`s premier design hotel. It offers sophisticated interiors, floor-to-ceiling windows, and one of the best rooftop bars in the Balkans. Guests enjoy stunning views of the Alexander Nevsky Cathedral and indulgent spa experiences.',180.0,396),
	 (81,12,'InterContinental Sofia','4 Narodno Sabranie Sq., 1000 Sofia, Bulgaria','Set in a landmark location next to the Parliament and Alexander Nevsky Cathedral, InterContinental Sofia combines contemporary style with discreet luxury. Perfect for business and leisure, it boasts spacious rooms, a chic bar, and award-winning hospitality.',200.0,401),
	 (82,12,'Grand Hotel Millennium Sofia','89B Vitosha Blvd, 1463 Sofia, Bulgaria','Towering over the city, this contemporary 30-story hotel offers unbeatable views of Vitosha Mountain. Grand Hotel Millennium features spacious rooms, multiple dining venues, a holistic wellness centre, and impressive event facilities — ideal for modern luxury seekers.',170.0,406),
	 (83,12,'Hyatt Regency Sofia','1 Vasil Levski Square, 1504 Sofia, Bulgaria','Situated near Sofia’s cultural heart, Hyatt Regency offers upscale comfort with contemporary interiors and exceptional service. Guests enjoy a rooftop bar, serene spa, and the Regency Club Lounge — all just steps from parks, museums, and monuments.',190.0,411),
	 (84,13,'Graffit Gallery Design Hotel','65 Knyaz Boris I Blvd, 9000 Varna, Bulgaria','Graffit Gallery Design Hotel is a modern and stylish hotel located in the heart of Varna. It features contemporary art-inspired interiors, spacious rooms, and a rooftop terrace with panoramic city views. Guests can enjoy gourmet dining at the hotel`s restaurant and relax at the wellness center.​',150.0,416),
	 (85,13,'Grand Hotel London','3 Musala Str, 9000 Varna, Bulgaria','Grand Hotel London is a historic hotel that combines classic elegance with modern comfort. Situated in the city center, it offers easy access to Varna`s main attractions. The hotel features luxurious rooms with antique furnishings, a refined restaurant, and a cozy bar.',140.0,421);
