	 (88,14,'Grand Hôtel Stockholm','Södra Blasieholmshamnen 8, 103 27 Stockholm, Sweden','Established in 1874, the Grand Hôtel Stockholm is a symbol of timeless elegance and luxury. Overlooking the Royal Palace and Gamla Stan, it offers guests opulent rooms, world-class dining, and a renowned spa. The hotel`s rich history and impeccable service make it a top choice for discerning travelers.',350.0,436),
	 (89,14,'Hotel Diplomat Stockholm','Strandvägen 7C, 114 56 Stockholm, Sweden','Situated in a stunning Art Nouveau building, Hotel Diplomat offers a blend of classic charm and modern luxury. Located on the prestigious Strandvägen boulevard, it provides easy access to Stockholm`s cultural attractions. Guests can enjoy elegantly designed rooms, a gourmet restaurant, and exceptional service.',300.0,441),
	 (90,14,'Nobis Hotel Stockholm','Norrmalmstorg 2-4, 111 86 Stockholm, Sweden','Located in the heart of Stockholm, Nobis Hotel combines historical architecture with contemporary design. Housed in two 19th-century buildings, it offers guests a sophisticated atmosphere, modern amenities, and proximity to shopping and cultural sites.',280.0,446),
	 (91,14,'Lydmar Hotel','Södra Blasieholmshamnen 2, 111 48 Stockholm, Sweden','Lydmar Hotel offers a unique boutique experience with its blend of classic and contemporary decor. Located near the Royal Castle and Nationalmuseum, it provides guests with stylish rooms, a vibrant restaurant, and a relaxed atmosphere. The hotel`s commitment to personalized service ensures a memorable stay.​',320.0,451),
	 (92,15,'Sankt Jörgen Park','Knipplekullen 8-10, 417 49 Gothenburg, Sweden','Nestled in lush greenery just outside central Gothenburg, Sankt Jörgen Park is a modern resort offering luxury and tranquility. With a world-class spa, award-winning golf course, and chic design, it’s perfect for both relaxation and active escapes. The peaceful setting provides a retreat from the city bustle.',230.0,456),
	 (93,15,'Hotel Pigalle','Södra Hamngatan 2A, 411 06 Gothenburg, Sweden','Hotel Pigalle is a romantic boutique hotel inspired by early 20th-century Paris. Each room is uniquely designed with vintage flair and luxury touches. Its intimate ambiance, acclaimed restaurant, and central location make it a favorite for stylish stays in Gothenburg.',220.0,461),
	 (94,15,'Upper House','Mässans Gata 24, 412 51 Gothenburg, Sweden','Upper House sits atop Gothia Towers, offering panoramic city views and sophisticated, Scandinavian-style luxury. Its award-winning spa, refined cuisine, and impeccable service make it one of Sweden’s finest urban retreats. Perfect for travelers seeking elegance and wellness.',300.0,466),
	 (95,15,'Hotel Riverton','Stora Badhusgatan 26, 411 21 Gothenburg, Sweden','Hotel Riverton is a sleek and stylish waterfront hotel with a modern Scandinavian design. Close to the harbor and Gothenburg’s historic center, it combines contemporary comfort with warm hospitality. The rooftop restaurant and serene spa are guest favorites.',190.0,471);
