	 (99,16,'Sofitel Cairo Nile El Gezirah','3 El Thawra Council St Zamalek, Cairo, Egypt','Situated on El Gezirah Island, Sofitel Cairo Nile El Gezirah offers panoramic views of the Nile. The hotel combines French luxury with Egyptian hospitality, featuring stylish rooms, gourmet dining, and a serene spa. Its central location allows easy access to Cairo`s attractions.',250.0,491),
	 (100,17,'Four Seasons Hotel Alexandria at San Stefano','399 El Geish Road, San Stefano, Alexandria, Egypt','Located on the Mediterranean coastline, the Four Seasons Hotel Alexandria at San Stefano offers guests a truly luxurious experience. The 19-story hotel is European-inspired and offers several al fresco restaurants, a private beach, and a lavish spa.',350.0,496),
	 (101,17,'Steigenberger Cecil Hotel','16 Saad Zagloul Square, Raml Station, Alexandria, Egypt','Steigenberger Cecil Hotel is a historic hotel offering old-world charm and romance. With a classical facade and grand interiors, it features an excellent French restaurant and is situated on the sea`s edge.',120.0,501),
	 (102,17,'Helnan Royal Hotel – Montazah Gardens','El Montazah Palace, Alexandria, Egypt','Surrounded by the lush greenery of Montazah Palace Gardens, this hotel offers guests a royal retreat by the sea. The ambiance is peaceful, elegant, and ideal for both leisure and romance. Classic interiors, a private beach, and elevated dining complete the experience.',110.0,506),
	 (103,17,'Le Metropole Luxury Heritage Hotel','52 Saad Zaghloul Street, Alexandria, Egypt','A historic gem dating back to 1902, Le Metropole offers timeless elegance with direct Corniche views. Enjoy rooftop breakfasts and rooms with antique decor and modern comfort.',100.0,511),
	 (104,18,'Four Seasons Hotel Casablanca','Anfa Place Boulevard de la Corniche, Casablanca, Morocco','Overlooking the Atlantic Ocean, the Four Seasons Casablanca offers a serene, resort-style experience just minutes from the city’s vibrant heart. With contemporary Moroccan décor, lush gardens, and sea-facing terraces, it’s the perfect mix of beachfront relaxation and urban sophistication. Whether enjoying fresh seafood by the waves or indulging in a hammam treatment, guests are immersed in luxury and tranquility.',350.0,516),
	 (105,18,'Sofitel Casablanca Tour Blanche','Rue Sidi Belyout, Casablanca, Morocco','Rising high above the port and Medina, the Sofitel Tour Blanche is a beacon of elegance where French art de vivre meets Moroccan warmth. With panoramic city and sea views, the hotel offers stylish rooms, a world-class spa, and award-winning cuisine. Ideal for business and leisure travelers alike, it’s known for its impeccable service, sophisticated atmosphere, and unbeatable location.',200.0,521);
INSERT INTO travel_db.hotels (gallery_id,city_id,name,location,about,price,preferred_gallery_entry_id) VALUES
	 (106,18,'Hyatt Regency Casablanca','Place des Nations Unies, Casablanca, Morocco','Located in the heart of the business district and steps from the Medina, the Hyatt Regency Casablanca offers timeless comfort with a cosmopolitan twist. The spacious rooms feature Art Deco accents and cityscape views. A lush outdoor pool, curated Moroccan dining, and vibrant public spaces make this a haven of relaxation and sophistication.',180.0,526),
	 (107,18,'Kenzi Tower Hotel','Twin Center, Casablanca, Morocco','Towering above the Casablanca skyline, Kenzi Tower Hotel is located in the iconic Twin Center and offers a refined and contemporary experience. Known for its breathtaking panoramic views, high-end service, and modern design, this hotel is a favorite among travelers seeking upscale comfort in the heart of the city. From fine dining on the 27th floor to tranquil spa escapes, it’s luxury with a modern Moroccan touch.',150.0,531),
	 (108,19,'Royal Mansour Marrakech','Rue Abou Abbas El Sebti, Medina, Marrakesh, Morocco','Commissioned by King Mohammed VI, Royal Mansour is a palatial oasis in the heart of Marrakesh. The hotel comprises 53 private riads, each with its own courtyard, rooftop terrace, and plunge pool, offering guests unparalleled privacy and luxury. The intricate Moroccan craftsmanship, lush gardens, and a world-class spa create an atmosphere of regal opulence.​',1000.0,536),
	 (109,19,'La Mamounia','Avenue Bab Jdid, Medina, Marrakesh, Morocco','La Mamounia is a legendary hotel that has hosted celebrities and dignitaries since 1923. Set within royal gardens, the hotel combines traditional Moroccan architecture with Art Deco design. Guests can enjoy opulent rooms, a luxurious spa, and exquisite dining options, all within walking distance of the city`s historic sites.​',500.0,541),
	 (110,19,'The Oberoi Marrakech','Route de Ouarzazate, Marrakesh, Morocco','The Oberoi Marrakech is a luxurious resort set amidst 28 acres of Mediterranean orchards and Andalusian-style gardens. The hotel`s architecture is inspired by traditional Moroccan palaces, featuring grand courtyards and intricate zellige tilework. Guests can indulge in spacious villas with private pools, a holistic spa, and gourmet dining experiences.​',600.0,546),
	 (111,19,'Amanjena','Route de Ouarzazate, Marrakesh, Morocco','Amanjena, meaning `peaceful paradise, ` is a serene resort located just outside Marrakesh. The resort`s design is inspired by traditional Moroccan architecture, featuring rose-hued walls, vaulted ceilings, and tranquil courtyards. Guests can enjoy spacious pavilions, a luxurious spa, and a championship golf course nearby.​',700.0,551),
	 (112,20,'Saxon Hotel, Villas & Spa','36 Saxon Road, Sandhurst, Johannesburg, South Africa','The Saxon Hotel, Villas & Spa is a luxurious retreat nestled in the tranquil suburb of Sandhurst. Known for its impeccable service and elegant design, the hotel offers spacious suites, private villas, and a world-class spa. Guests can enjoy fine dining experiences and lush gardens, making it a perfect oasis in the city.​',600.0,556),
	 (113,20,'Four Seasons Hotel The Westcliff','67 Jan Smuts Avenue, Westcliff, Johannesburg, South Africa','Perched on a hillside in the prestigious Westcliff neighborhood, Four Seasons Hotel The Westcliff offers panoramic views of the city’s lush canopy. The hotel combines contemporary elegance with classic charm, featuring spacious rooms, a luxurious spa, and exceptional dining options.​',500.0,561),
	 (114,20,'The Michelangelo Hotel','135 West Street, Sandton, Johannesburg, South Africa','Located in the heart of Sandton, The Michelangelo Hotel is a symbol of luxury and sophistication. With its Renaissance architecture and opulent interiors, the hotel offers guests an unparalleled experience. Its proximity to Nelson Mandela Square and Sandton City Mall makes it an ideal choice for both leisure and business travelers.​',400.0,566),
	 (115,20,'The Peech Hotel','61 North Street, Melrose, Johannesburg, South Africa','The Peech Hotel is a chic boutique hotel situated in the leafy suburb of Melrose. Known for its eco-friendly practices and contemporary design, the hotel offers a tranquil escape with beautifully landscaped gardens and stylish rooms. Its commitment to sustainability and personalized service makes it a favorite among discerning travelers.​',300.0,571);
INSERT INTO travel_db.hotels (gallery_id,city_id,name,location,about,price,preferred_gallery_entry_id) VALUES
	 (116,21,'One&Only Cape Town','Dock Road, V&A Waterfront, Cape Town, South Africa','Nestled in the heart of the V&A Waterfront, One&Only Cape Town offers a luxurious urban resort experience with breathtaking views of Table Mountain. The hotel features spacious rooms and suites, world-class dining options including Nobu, and a serene spa on a private island. Guests can enjoy personalized service and easy access to Cape Town`s top attractions. ',750.0,576),
	 (117,21,'The Silo Hotel','Silo Square, V&A Waterfront, Cape Town, South Africa','Perched above the Zeitz Museum of Contemporary Art Africa, The Silo Hotel is an architectural marvel offering unparalleled views of the city and harbor. Each room is uniquely designed with floor-to-ceiling windows, showcasing Cape Town`s beauty. Guests can indulge in the rooftop pool, spa treatments, and exquisite dining experiences. ',1200.0,581),
	 (118,21,'Ellerman House','180 Kloof Road, Bantry Bay, Cape Town, South Africa','Situated in the exclusive Bantry Bay area, Ellerman House is a luxurious boutique hotel offering panoramic views of the Atlantic Ocean. The property boasts an extensive South African art collection, a world-class wine gallery, and elegant accommodations. Guests can enjoy personalized service, tranquil gardens, and proximity to Cape Town`s beaches. ',900.0,586),
	 (119,21,'Mount Nelson, A Belmond Hotel','76 Orange Street, Gardens, Cape Town, South Africa','A historic landmark since 1899, Mount Nelson offers timeless elegance in the heart of Cape Town. Set against the backdrop of Table Mountain, the hotel features lush gardens, classic architecture, and a renowned afternoon tea service. Guests can relax in spacious rooms, enjoy the spa, and explore nearby cultural attractions.',500.0,591),
	 (120,22,'Villa Rosa Kempinski','Chiromo Road, Nairobi, Kenya','Villa Rosa Kempinski is a luxurious 5-star hotel situated in the heart of Nairobi. The hotel boasts beautiful and spacious rooms, a rooftop pool, various dining options, a spa, and a gym. Its superb service and luxurious amenities distinguish it from other hotels in the city.',200.0,596),
	 (121,22,'Hemingways Nairobi','Mbagathi Ridge, Karen, Nairobi, Kenya','Hemingways Nairobi is a boutique hotel located in the serene suburb of Karen. Known for its colonial charm, personalized service, and stunning views of the Ngong Hills, the hotel offers a tranquil escape from the bustling city.',250.0,601),
	 (122,22,'Giraffe Manor','Langata Road, Nairobi, Kenya','Giraffe Manor is an exclusive boutique hotel set in 12 acres of private land within 140 acres of indigenous forest in the Langata suburb of Nairobi. It`s famous for its resident herd of Rothschild giraffes that visit the manor in the mornings and evenings, poking their heads into the windows in the hope of a treat.',800.0,606),
	 (123,22,'Fairmont The Norfolk','Harry Thuku Road, Nairobi, Kenya','Fairmont The Norfolk is a historic hotel that has been a cornerstone of Nairobi`s hospitality since 1904. The hotel combines classic elegance with modern amenities, offering guests a unique blend of heritage and luxury.',180.0,611),
	 (124,23,'Zannier Hotels Omaanda','Zannier Reserve, near Windhoek, Namibia','Zannier Hotels Omaanda is a boutique lodge set in the heart of the Zannier Reserve, a 22,000-acre wildlife conservancy located half an hour from Windhoek. The property features traditional Owambo architecture and elevated views stretching across soul-stirring savannas to the distant Khomas Hochland plateau. Accommodation consists of 10 individual thatch and clay huts, each with their own sunken bathtub and panoramic terrace. Guests can enjoy unique experiences like breakfast with meerkats at sunrise, tracking rhinos or elephants, and observing leopards in their natural habitat.',800.0,616),
	 (125,23,'Hotel Heinitzburg','22 Heinitzburg Street, Windhoek, Namibia','Hotel Heinitzburg is a restored castle with unique architecture, set on top of a hill in Windhoek. It features a pool in a manicured garden, a wine cellar, and two restaurants. The rooms are gracefully decorated with classic finishes. Heinitzburg’s gourmet restaurant, Leo’s at the Castle, overlooks the skyline of the city and offers an à la carte menu. The Garden Terrace with views of the surrounding mountains serves snacks and refreshments. Guests can relax on sun loungers around the swimming pool.',250.0,621);
INSERT INTO travel_db.hotels (gallery_id,city_id,name,location,about,price,preferred_gallery_entry_id) VALUES
	 (126,23,'The Weinberg Windhoek','13 Jan Jonker Road, Klein Windhoek, Namibia','The Weinberg Windhoek is a restored estate with unique architecture, set on top of a hill in Windhoek. It features a pool in a manicured garden, a wine cellar, and two restaurants. The rooms are gracefully decorated with classic finishes. Guests can relax on sun loungers around the swimming pool.',200.0,626),
	 (127,23,'Windhoek Country Club Resort','Western Bypass, Windhoek, Namibia','The Windhoek Country Club Resort is a 4-star hotel in the Namibian capital Windhoek. It is operated by the South African Legacy Group but is state-owned by the Ministry of Environment and Tourism. The hotel was opened in 1995 for the Miss Namibia and Miss Universe pageants. It is considered one of the best hotels in the country and has won numerous national awards. The hotel is designed as a country club and, in addition to the hotel building with 152 rooms and suites, four restaurants and bars, has an 18-hole golf course and a large pool area. The hotel also has the Oryx Conference Centre, the second largest conference center in Namibia.',150.0,631),
	 (128,24,'L`Escale Resort Marina & Spa – Small Luxury Hotels of the World','Roche Caiman, Victoria, Mahé, Seychelles','L`Escale Resort Marina & Spa is a boutique luxury resort situated near Victoria, offering panoramic views of the marina and surrounding mountains. The resort features elegantly designed rooms and suites, a full-service spa, and a fine dining restaurant. Guests can enjoy personalized services and easy access to the capital`s attractions.',450.0,636),
	 (129,24,'Hilton Seychelles Northolme Resort & Spa','Glacis, Victoria, Mahé, Seychelles','Perched on the hillside of Glacis, Hilton Seychelles Northolme Resort & Spa offers stunning ocean views and a tranquil atmosphere. The resort features private villas with infinity pools, a luxurious spa, and multiple dining options. It`s an ideal retreat for those seeking privacy and relaxation.',500.0,641),
	 (130,24,'Hilltop Boutique Hotel','Serret Road, St Louis, Victoria, Mahé, Seychelles','Hilltop Boutique Hotel is a charming property located on a hillside overlooking Victoria. The hotel offers spacious rooms with balconies, providing panoramic views of the city and ocean. Guests appreciate the personalized service and convenient location near the capital`s attractions.',200.0,646),
	 (131,24,'Carana Beach Hotel','North Coast Road, Glacis, Victoria, Mahé, Seychelles','CaranaBeach Hotel is a boutique beachfront property offering contemporary chalets with private terraces. The hotel features a beachfront pool, a spa, and a restaurant serving Creole-inspired cuisine. Guests enjoy the serene setting and direct access to the beach.',300.0,651),
	 (132,25,'Savoy Seychelles Resort & Spa','Beau Vallon, Mahé, Seychelles','Savoy Seychelles Resort & Spa is a luxurious beachfront resort located in the heart of Beau Vallon Bay, renowned for its pristine beaches and crystal-clear waters. The resort offers spacious rooms and suites with modern amenities, private balconies, and stunning ocean views. Guests can indulge in a variety of dining options, relax by the expansive outdoor pool, or rejuvenate at the full-service spa. The resort`s prime location provides easy access to local attractions and water sports activities.',300.0,656),
	 (133,25,'STORY Seychelles','Bel Ombre Road, Beau Vallon, Mahé, Seychelles','STORY Seychelles is a boutique resort nestled along the white sands of Beau Vallon Beach. The resort features elegantly designed villas and suites, each with private terraces and contemporary décor. Guests can enjoy a range of dining experiences, from fine dining to beachside grills, and partake in various recreational activities including snorkeling and kayaking. The resort`s tranquil setting and attentive service make it a perfect retreat for couples and families alike.​',350.0,661),
	 (134,25,'Fisherman`s Cove Resort','Bel Ombre, Beau Vallon, Mahé, Seychelles','Fisherman`s Cove Resort is one of Seychelles` original hotels, offering a blend of traditional charm and modern comfort. Situated at the end of Beau Vallon Beach, the resort provides breathtaking views of the Indian Ocean. Guests can relax in well-appointed rooms and suites, dine at the resort`s signature restaurants, or unwind at the infinity pool. The resort`s serene ambiance and rich history provide a unique and memorable stay.',280.0,666),
	 (135,25,'Coral Strand Smart Choice Hotel','Beau Vallon, Mahé, Seychelles','Coral Strand Smart Choice Hotel offers a comfortable and affordable beachfront accommodation in Beau Vallon. The hotel features modern rooms with sea or mountain views, multiple dining options including a sushi bar, and a beachfront pool. Its central location makes it convenient for guests to explore local markets, restaurants, and engage in various water sports. The hotel is ideal for travelers seeking value without compromising on location and essential amenities.',200.0,671);
INSERT INTO travel_db.hotels (gallery_id,city_id,name,location,about,price,preferred_gallery_entry_id) VALUES
	 (136,26,'Waldorf Astoria Beverly Hills','9850 Wilshire Blvd, Beverly Hills, CA 90210','The Waldorf Astoria Beverly Hills epitomizes luxury with its elegant design, rooftop pool, and panoramic views of Los Angeles. Guests can indulge in fine dining at Jean-Georges Beverly Hills and unwind at the on-site La Prairie Spa. Its prime location offers easy access to Rodeo Drive and other Beverly Hills attractions.',1000.0,676),
	 (137,26,'Hotel Bel-Air','701 Stone Canyon Rd, Los Angeles, CA 90077','Nestled in the hills of Bel-Air, this iconic hotel offers a serene retreat with its lush gardens and swan lake. The Hotel Bel-Air combines classic Hollywood glamour with modern luxury, featuring spacious rooms, a renowned spa, and Wolfgang Puck`s signature restaurant.',900.0,681),
	 (138,26,'The Beverly Hills Hotel','9641 Sunset Blvd, Beverly Hills, CA 90210','Known as "The Pink Palace," The Beverly Hills Hotel has been a symbol of glamour since 1912. Guests can enjoy luxurious bungalows, a legendary pool, and the famous Polo Lounge. Its rich history and timeless elegance make it a favorite among celebrities and discerning travelers.',950.0,686),
	 (139,26,'Conrad Los Angeles','100 S Grand Ave, Los Angeles, CA 90012','Located in downtown Los Angeles, the Conrad offers modern luxury with its sleek design and panoramic city views. The hotel features multiple dining options, a rooftop pool, and close proximity to cultural landmarks like the Walt Disney Concert Hall.',750.0,691),
	 (140,27,'The Ritz-Carlton New York, NoMad','25 W 28th St, New York, NY 10001','The Ritz-Carlton New York, NoMad is a towering, 50-story beacon of luxury in the rapidly changing neighborhood just north of Madison Square Park. It offers gorgeously appointed rooms with stunning views, excellent dining options, and the above-and-beyond hospitality that’s associated with the brand.',1100.0,696),
	 (141,27,'The Plaza Hotel','768 5th Ave, New York, NY 10019','The Plaza Hotel, an iconic landmark at the corner of Fifth Avenue and Central Park South, offers a blend of timeless elegance and modern luxury. Guests can indulge in spacious rooms with classic decor, world-class dining, and the renowned Palm Court for afternoon tea.',1200.0,701),
	 (142,27,'Four Seasons Hotel New York Downtown','27 Barclay St, New York, NY 10007','Located in Lower Manhattan, the Four Seasons Hotel New York Downtown offers contemporary luxury with spacious rooms, a full-service spa, and an indoor lap pool. Its proximity to the Financial District and Tribeca makes it ideal for both business and leisure travelers.',1000.0,706),
	 (143,27,'The St. Regis New York','2 E 55th St, New York, NY 10022','The St. Regis New York, situated in Midtown Manhattan, epitomizes refined luxury with its Beaux-Arts architecture and bespoke butler service. Guests can enjoy elegantly appointed rooms, the famed King Cole Bar, and exceptional personalized services.',1150.0,711),
	 (144,28,'Wynn Las Vegas','3131 Las Vegas Blvd S, Las Vegas, NV 89109','Wynn Las Vegas is renowned for its opulent design, top-tier service, and a plethora of amenities. Guests can enjoy spacious rooms with floor-to-ceiling windows, a variety of fine dining options, and a vibrant casino. The resort also features luxury shopping, a world-class spa, and an 18-hole golf course.',600.0,716),
	 (145,28,'The Venetian Resort Las Vegas','3355 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109','The Venetian Resort offers a taste of Italy in the heart of Las Vegas. Guests can enjoy spacious suites, gondola rides along the Grand Canal, and a wide array of dining options. The resort also boasts a state-of-the-art casino, luxury shopping at the Grand Canal Shoppes, and a world-class spa.',500.0,721);
INSERT INTO travel_db.hotels (gallery_id,city_id,name,location,about,price,preferred_gallery_entry_id) VALUES
	 (146,28,'ARIA Resort & Casino','3730 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89158','ARIA Resort & Casino is a modern luxury destination known for its sleek design and cutting-edge technology. Guests can enjoy smart rooms with automated controls, a variety of dining options from renowned chefs, and a vibrant nightlife scene. The resort also features a large casino, multiple pools, and a full-service spa.',450.0,726),
