	 (149,29,'The Ritz-Carlton, Toronto','181 Wellington St W, Toronto, ON M5V 3G7','Situated in the heart of downtown, The Ritz-Carlton offers luxurious accommodations with views of Lake Ontario and the city skyline. Guests can enjoy the hotel`s spa, fine dining at TOCA, and proximity to the CN Tower and entertainment district.',650.0,741),
	 (150,29,'The Hazelton Hotel','118 Yorkville Ave, Toronto, ON M5R 1C2','As Canada`s first and only Forbes Five-Star independent luxury boutique hotel, The Hazelton Hotel is located in the fashionable Yorkville area. It features spacious rooms, a private screening room, and the renowned ONE Restaurant by Chef Mark McEwan.',600.0,746),
	 (151,29,'Shangri-La Hotel, Toronto','188 University Ave, Toronto, ON M5H 0A3','The Shangri-La Hotel combines Asian-inspired elegance with contemporary design. Located between the financial and entertainment districts, it offers luxurious rooms, a tranquil spa, and dining at Bosk Restaurant. The hotel also features a lobby lounge with live music and afternoon tea service.',550.0,751),
	 (152,30,'Fairmont Pacific Rim','1038 Canada Pl, Vancouver, BC V6C 0B9','The Fairmont Pacific Rim offers a waterfront location with stunning views of the harbor and mountains. The hotel blends modern luxury with nature, featuring an award-winning spa, top-tier dining, and an exceptional rooftop pool. Guests can unwind at the Botanist Restaurant or relax at the Willow Stream Spa for a truly luxurious experience.',650.0,756),
	 (153,30,'Rosewood Hotel Georgia','801 W Georgia St, Vancouver, BC V6C 1P7','The Rosewood Hotel Georgia combines historic charm with modern luxury in the heart of Vancouver. This iconic hotel is known for its elegant rooms, exceptional service, and fine dining at the renowned Hawksworth Restaurant. Whether you’re unwinding in the Sense spa or enjoying afternoon tea, this hotel offers a sophisticated escape.',700.0,761),
	 (154,30,'Shangri-La Hotel Vancouver','1128 W Georgia St, Vancouver, BC V6E 0A8','Shangri-La Hotel Vancouver offers a combination of luxury, modern elegance, and a prime downtown location. The hotel features stunning views, a tranquil spa, and Asian-inspired cuisine at Bosk Restaurant. Shangri-La also offers a spacious fitness center, an outdoor pool, and an executive lounge for business travelers.',550.0,766),
	 (155,30,'Wedgewood Hotel & Spa','845 Hornby St, Vancouver, BC V6Z 1V1','Wedgewood Hotel & Spa is a boutique luxury hotel in downtown Vancouver, known for its intimate and elegant atmosphere. Guests can enjoy personalized service, fine dining at the Bacchus Restaurant, and a relaxing experience at the Spa at Wedgewood. This charming hotel offers a blend of European luxury and modern amenities.',600.0,771);
