	 (161,32,'Le Blanc Spa Resort Cancun','Blvd. Kukulcan Km 10, Zona Hotelera, 77500 Cancún, Q.R.','Le Blanc Spa Resort sets the standard for luxury all-inclusive experiences in Cancún. With its minimalist white design, impeccable service, and world-class dining, it`s a peaceful oasis for adult travelers seeking total indulgence.',850.0,801),
	 (162,33,'InterContinental Real Santo Domingo','Av. Winston Churchill 93, Ensanche Piantini, 10127 Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic','Located in the heart of Santo Domingo’s business and entertainment district, InterContinental Real Santo Domingo offers modern luxury with panoramic city views. With a stunning infinity pool, fine dining restaurants, and an exceptional spa, it’s a perfect choice for both business and leisure travelers.',380.0,806),
	 (163,33,'JW Marriott Hotel Santo Domingo','Av. Winston Churchill, Blue Mall, 10127 Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic','The JW Marriott Hotel Santo Domingo brings contemporary sophistication to the Caribbean’s oldest city. Connected directly to Blue Mall, the hotel offers luxurious rooms, an impressive rooftop infinity pool, gourmet dining, and personalized service, setting a new standard of elegance in the capital.',420.0,811),
	 (164,34,'Tortuga Bay Hotel at Puntacana Resort & Club','Punta Cana Resort & Club, 23000 Punta Cana, Dominican Republic','Designed by Oscar de la Renta, Tortuga Bay offers an ultra-luxurious, intimate beachfront experience. With elegant villas, personalized service, and access to a private beach and world-class golf courses, it’s the ultimate Caribbean escape for discerning travelers.',1000.0,816),
