	 (170,36,'Rosewood Beijing','Jing Guang Centre, Hujialou, Chaoyang District, Beijing, China','Rosewood Beijing is a serene urban retreat that blends residential elegance with contemporary Chinese style. Offering sophisticated accommodations, six outstanding dining venues, and a world-class spa, it sets a new benchmark for luxury in the capital city.',580.0,846),
	 (171,36,'The Peninsula Beijing','8 Goldfish Lane, Wangfujing, Dongcheng District, Beijing, China','The Peninsula Beijing seamlessly combines traditional Chinese artistry with modern luxury. With all-suite accommodations, world-class dining, and impeccable service, it provides an exquisite experience steps away from the Forbidden City and Tiananmen Square.',750.0,851),
	 (172,37,'The Peninsula Shanghai','32 Zhongshan East 1st Rd, The Bund, Huangpu District, Shanghai, China','Set directly on Shanghai’s historic Bund, The Peninsula Shanghai combines Art Deco glamour with impeccable service. Offering breathtaking views of the Huangpu River and Pudong skyline, it features luxurious suites, award-winning dining, and the finest spa facilities.',720.0,856),
	 (173,37,'Waldorf Astoria Shanghai on the Bund','2 Zhongshan East 1st Rd, The Bund, Huangpu District, Shanghai, China','A legendary address on the Bund, Waldorf Astoria Shanghai merges historic elegance with modern luxury. Once the famed Shanghai Club, today it offers opulent suites, world-class dining, and a perfect blend of heritage and contemporary sophistication.',650.0,861),
	 (174,38,'The Leela Palace New Delhi','Diplomatic Enclave, Chanakyapuri, New Delhi, India','The Leela Palace New Delhi offers opulent grandeur inspired by Lutyens’ architecture and Indian royalty. With lavish rooms, gourmet dining, a rooftop pool, and an award-winning spa, it provides a palatial stay in the heart of India`s bustling capital.',500.0,866),
