	 (181,41,'Four Seasons Resort Bali at Sayan','Sayan, Ubud, Bali 80571, Indonesia','Set amidst the lush rice paddies and tropical jungle of Ubud, Four Seasons Resort Bali at Sayan is a serene hideaway offering luxury, wellness, and nature in harmony. Featuring luxurious villas, a riverside spa, and exceptional dining, it’s a true Bali sanctuary.',800.0,901),
	 (182,42,'Mandarin Oriental, Bangkok','48 Oriental Ave, Khwaeng Bang Rak, Bang Rak, Bangkok 10500, Thailand','An icon of timeless elegance on the banks of the Chao Phraya River, Mandarin Oriental, Bangkok offers legendary service, luxurious suites, and a rich heritage dating back over 145 years. It’s a perfect blend of history, sophistication, and Thai charm.',650.0,906),
